=== v0.5.2 release — 2026-04-26 (operator config tree expansion) ===

Surfaced fifteen previously-buried operator tunables in the
/etc/blacklight/blacklight.conf preflight loader. Audit motivation: the
landed default config exposed only 7 of ~22 runtime-effective BL_* env
knobs; operator could not configure log verbosity, the LLM kill switch,
defend's ASN/CDN/CIDR-floor levers, clean's TTL/grace, observe's journal
cap, scanner sig dirs, or the alt skill repo without setting env vars per
invocation. No runtime behaviour changes for unconfigured operators —
every new key is opt-in and defaults exactly to the source-level
${BL_<KEY>:-default} fallback.

